<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="78166">
Russia. Murmansk Region. Lovozero District. Revda Village (SW part), close to the museum buildings, 02.08.2011, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="78166">M. Piirainen</emphasis>
6061 (H 827871).
</paragraph>
